profile_positions.description:
During this time I held various positions within Infosys BPM Eindhoven:
- member of the management team;
- group leader for a team of financial controllers;
- quality manager / information security officer / risk manager / compliance officer;
- financial controller for a group of supply chain related departments within Philips Healthcare
-in this period I was asked to participate in the Geo Ambassador program of Infosys. This is an Infosys leadership program that is held periodically in Mysore, India.
